The app is a game, emulating the board game ricchocet robots.
Players can invite friends to a multi-round game of Dinos.
The goal of each round is to be the player who can get the designated dino to the goal square in the least number of dino moves.
Each round the winner is awareded 1 point for having the least moves. A game is over when all players ahs submitted moves for each round. The winner is the player with the most points across all rounds.